{"tid":2150870,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"躁情侶罵示威者兼打人判社會服務令 離庭罵記者「黑記 曱甴」","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:14:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e034b7b08d4fc2f2ec46a0fbe8a4835e1b8cd4f3","tid":2150870,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/OS3U4GI4M2WFFDAP6DCGCQ5W74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FOS3U4GI4M2WFFDAP6DCGCQ5W74%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=20e99a47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FOS3U4GI4M2WFFDAP6DCGCQ5W74%2F&h=4395145a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/OS3U4GI4M2WFFDAP6DCGCQ5W74/</a><br />\n<br />\n姊弟戀同居情侶去年8月清晨醉酒後，在將軍澳辱罵示威者為「曱甴」並襲擊途人。其間四名途人欲調停，卻遭女方發難以手掌及拖鞋施襲，男友亦出手「護花」打人，最終五人遇襲受傷。肇事情侶早前承認六項普通襲擊罪，主任裁判官徐綺薇今分別判兩人履行180及100小時社會服務令。惟女被告離庭時未有改口，辱罵在場記者為「黑記，曱甴」，身旁男親友更衝撞記者，阻止拍攝。"},{"pid":"849fdc4423970aa3e595ade945934271429e3ded","tid":2150870,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8013&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=ce5dec76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8013</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官 <br />\n<br />\n#不是聲援 <br />\n<br />\n江詠虹(49)、李朝偉(38)（#0828將軍澳 稱呼示威者為曱甴，及後與一名男食客發生爭執）<br />\n<br />\n兩份報告正面，被告皆同意報告內容。<br />\n<br />\n辯方再指D1受酒精影響犯案，D2一心希望協助太太，辯方希望法庭採納社會服務令報告建議。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官宣判前指認為被告失去理智，加上考慮求情信等，認同本次應為個別事件。考慮到社會服務令報告正面、D1還押3星期、沒有預謀，幸好受害人傷勢不算嚴重。<br />\n<br />\nD1的5項襲擊罪判處180小時社會服務令，同期執行，D2 判處100小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"f7d8d83b73d8c07e262077b1414420f01e4dd5d5","tid":2150870,"uid":60831,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"6條罪都唔洗坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce50269e3a420df3a7bd291c4377f4b33178e14","tid":2150870,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"出佢樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6782c84c985e7115d23465ae15c3c7f2bcbaac","tid":2150870,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hodor~hodor~"},{"pid":"88d2d83d9c3a79396cd51ea2715109c7301e9dfb","tid":2150870,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"買多左蘋果既手足 唔好齋擺屋企 當派報紙咁直頭擺去隔離鄰舍門口！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2150861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2150861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e05ab8a50163611aa718fc11c518cf8fdcd4c16","tid":2150870,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"鬧埋法官啦 笨㭍"},{"pid":"2ee058afe0a24bfa5562bd5dd7411638192f6394","tid":2150870,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7d8d83b73d8c07e262077b1414420f01e4dd5d5","tid":2150870,"uid":60831,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"6條罪都唔洗坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"無刀渣, 有刀就高尚情操 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236eb11a44e0bf636d968ad17c11bd04314a9e2f","tid":2150870,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:19:3